basics.label: Student
basics.summary: I am studying for a B.S. in Computer Engineering in the College of Engineering at the University of Hawaii. I expect to graduate in Spring, 2019. After graduation, I plan to pursue a career as a software engineer.

Extensive use of industry standard technologies such as React and Node.js to develop premium web experiences that drive online sales. Development work includes promotional Diablo Necromancer material and a redesigned Hearthstone eSports page.
